{
  "annotations": {"list": []},
  "editable": true,
  "schemaVersion": 30,
  "version": 1,
  "uid": "fraud-detection-overview",
  "title": "Fraud Detection — Project Overview",
  "tags": ["fraud", "overview", "executive"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "10s",
  "time": {"from": "now-1h", "to": "now"},
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "API status",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 4, "h": 4},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "up{job=\"fraud-detection-api\"}", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {"options": {"0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"}}, "type": "value"},
            {"options": {"1": {"text": "UP",   "color": "green"}}, "type": "value"}
          ],
          "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "green", "value": 1}]}
        }
      },
      "options": {"colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "textMode": "value"}
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Total predictions",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 4, "y": 0, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum(predictions_total) OR on() vector(0)", "refId": "A"}],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "blue", "value": null}]}}
      },
      "options": {"colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "textMode": "value_and_name"}
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Fraud caught",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 9, "y": 0, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [{"expr": "sum(predictions_total{result=\"fraud\"}) OR on() vector(0)", "refId": "A"}],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"},
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}]}}
      },
      "options": {"colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "textMode": "value_and_name"}
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Real-world accuracy",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 14, "y": 0, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [{"expr": "model_real_accuracy", "refId": "A"}],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "percentunit", "min": 0, "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "red", "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.7},
            {"color": "green", "value": 0.85}]}}
      },
      "options": {"colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "textMode": "value_and_name"}
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "Inference latency p99",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": {"x": 19, "y": 0, "w": 5, "h": 4},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(prediction_latency_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "s",
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green", "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.1},
            {"color": "red", "value": 0.2}]}}
      },
      "options": {"colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "area", "textMode": "value_and_name"}
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "Predictions / second (legit vs fraud)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "rate(predictions_total[1m])", "legendFormat": "{{result}}", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "reqps", "color": {"mode": "palette-classic"}}},
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom"}, "tooltip": {"mode": "multi"}}
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "Fraud ratio (rolling)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 12, "y": 4, "w": 12, "h": 8},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "fraud_ratio", "legendFormat": "fraud ratio", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "percentunit",
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green", "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 0.05},
            {"color": "red", "value": 0.10}]},
          "custom": {"thresholdsStyle": {"mode": "line+area"}}}
      },
      "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom"}, "tooltip": {"mode": "single"}}
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Host CPU usage",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 12, "w": 8, "h": 7},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "100 - (avg(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[1m])) * 100)", "legendFormat": "CPU %", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green", "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 70},
            {"color": "red", "value": 90}]}}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "Host memory used",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 8, "y": 12, "w": 8, "h": 7},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "(node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes) / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes * 100",
         "legendFormat": "RAM %", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green", "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 75},
            {"color": "red", "value": 90}]}}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "title": "Disk usage on /",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": {"x": 16, "y": 12, "w": 8, "h": 7},
      "datasource": "Prometheus",
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "(1 - node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\"} / node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint=\"/\"}) * 100",
         "legendFormat": "Disk %", "refId": "A"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {"unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [
            {"color": "green", "value": null},
            {"color": "yellow", "value": 75},
            {"color": "red", "value": 90}]}}
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "title": "Quick links",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": {"x": 0, "y": 19, "w": 24, "h": 4},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Project surfaces\n- **Streamlit UI** — http://localhost:8501\n- **API docs (Swagger)** — http://localhost:8000/docs\n- **MLflow Tracking + Registry** — http://localhost:5000\n- **Airflow (DAG console)** — http://localhost:8090\n- **Prometheus (raw metrics)** — http://localhost:9090\n- **AlertManager** — http://localhost:9093\n\n### Other dashboards in this folder\n- **API — Endpoint Detail** — per-handler latency, status codes, request/response size\n- **System Resources Detail** — per-CPU, memory pressure, disk I/O, network, file descriptors\n- **Stack Health** — `up{}` per scrape target, scrape duration, API process metrics\n- **ML Ops & Feedback Loop** — feedback rate, accuracy trend, label distribution"
      }
    }
  ]
}
